{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fd8e32c28a","title":"对叶群检讨信的几条批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4c9c51fb3","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"fd8e32c28a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d6878f563f","type":"title","text":"对叶群检讨信的几条批注","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5dc09f4233","type":"paragraph","text":"对叶群检讨信的几条批注","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d638c45120","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e915ecb45","type":"paragraph","text":"1970.10.15","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bc3b3ce66","type":"paragraph","text":"思想上政治上的路线正确与否是决定一切的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c97c5abe99","type":"paragraph","text":"爱吹不爱批，爱听小道消息，经不起风浪。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd1a9732e4","type":"paragraph","text":"一个倾向掩盖着另一个倾向。九大胜利，当上了中央委员，不得了了，要上天了，把九大路线抛到九霄云外，反九大的陈伯达路线在一些同志中占了上风了。请同志们研究一下，是不是这样的呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f78ed8983","type":"paragraph","text":"多年来不赞成读马、列的同志们，为何这时又向马、列求救，题目又是所谓论天才。不是在九大论过了吗，为何健忘若此？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f7d8c1a0a","type":"paragraph","text":"不提九大，不提党章。也不听我的话。陈伯达一吹，就上劲了。军委办事组好些同志都是如此。党的政策是惩前毖后，治病救人，除了陈伯达待审查外，凡上当者都适用。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fd8e32c28a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}